snippet.title: Captain Velvet Meteor : The Jump+ Dimensions - Trailer #2 English Version
snippet.description:
Captain Velvet Meteor: The Jump+ Dimensions is a tactical action game where we meet Damien, a young boy who's just moved to Japan. Lonely, Damien plunges into his imagination as the superhero Captain Velvet Meteor, and discovers a world of heroes and villains from his favourite manga. Call upon a roster of Jump+ characters to help him on his quest to escape the mysterious world and defeat an unknown menace! 

See more on : https://www.momo-pi.com/
